	(text "The parallelogram shape, clocked 90-deg, allows for the same mounting location.\nShould we reverse the pinout, or not?\nThe connectors have pins on top and bottom.\n\nDesigned-for clocking is, as-pictured in pcb layout, this is the right half.\nYou clock 90-deg counter-clockwise for the left half."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
